      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what do you mean by goblin raid? i just wanted the science part. can you just stick to the actual biochemistry of the glycolysis process? i dont really get how the lactate is actually cleared out of the bloodstream specifically.",
      "source": "evaluator"
